origin_prompt.content:
你能够调用以下的API:
[['PolygonFinance.get_ticker_news', {'name': 'PolygonFinance.get_ticker_news', 'description': 'get the most recent news articles relating to a stock ticker symbol', 'required_parameters': [], 'optional_parameters': [{'name': 'ticker', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'Return results that contain this ticker'}], 'return_data': [{'name': 'results', 'description': 'A list of news including title, summary, and author'}]}], ['CurrencyExchange.get_exchange_rate_history', {'name': 'CurrencyExchange.get_exchange_rate_history', 'description': 'Get the historical exchange rate for a currency pair over a specified number of days.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'currencyPair', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The currency pair in the format of CUR1/CUR2.'}, {'name': 'days', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The number of days to retrieve history for.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'rates', 'description': 'A list of exchange rates over the specified days.'}]}], ['StockMarket.get_index_data', {'name': 'StockMarket.get_index_data', 'description': 'Get the current data for a specified stock market index.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'index', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the stock market index.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'currentValue', 'description': 'The current value of the index.'}, {'name': 'percentageChange', 'description': 'The percentage change in the index value.'}]}], ['FinancialNews.get_news_by_topic', {'name': 'FinancialNews.get_news_by_topic', 'description': 'Get the latest financial news articles related to a specific topic.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'topic', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The topic to search news for.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'newsArticles', 'description': 'A list of news articles including title, summary, and publication date.'}]}], ['InvestmentAdvisor.provide_investment_advice', {'name': 'InvestmentAdvisor.provide_investment_advice', 'description': 'Provide investment advice based on recent policy changes and market reactions.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'index', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The stock market index to provide advice for.'}, {'name': 'policyChanges', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'Recent policy changes affecting the market.'}, {'name': 'marketReactions', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'Recent market reactions to the policy changes.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'advice', 'description': 'Investment advice based on the provided context.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `api1` 并传入 `arg1` 和 `arg2`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "api1",
    "args": "{'arg1': 'value1', 'arg2': 'value2', ...}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
